{"tid":895118,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"馬凱被拒入境　FCC稱震驚　重申要求港府立即解釋","createTime":"2018-11-09T02:42:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T11:42:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":55,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"cd3875ab4046b2b04fb68d28634b09632185a3b9","tid":895118,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:42:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181109/s00001/9ee7dccdc77ff4d7c554d9040bad6410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F9ee7dccdc77ff4d7c554d9040bad6410.jpg&h=eea284d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任職《金融時報》的外國記者會（FCC）第一副主席馬凱（Victor Mallet）昨午（8日）以旅客身分來港，但在接受本港入境處人員查問數小時後，被拒絕入境，FCC表示對此事感到震驚和困惑，重申要求港府立即解釋有關做法。<br />\n<br />\nFCC發表聲明指出，自從馬凱10月初被拒工作簽證續期，該會一直要求港府提供合理解釋，但不得要領。<br />\n<br />\nFCC指有關做法把在香港工作的新聞工作者置於不透明的環境中，當中恐懼和自我審查可能取代了自由和信心，而自由和信心對自由社會是至關重要的，也是受到基本法保障的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181109/s00001/1541730474026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F1541730474026&d=G9rguUQjZKtPcM8sTPrYkaMP9SZiTpIcsXSGftWU1%2BE%3D&h=94eb27e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181109%2Fs00001%2F1541730474026&h=d3dbbea4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181109/s00001/1541730474026</a>"},{"pid":"5f1943fe7188d54b42fd059fbd81732fb6c0bcbb","tid":895118,"uid":5995,"like":3,"dislike":42,"score":-39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:44:05.000Z","msg":"抵死"},{"pid":"66c1fab75cf86beda56951649ec845413175f627","tid":895118,"uid":195334,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T02:45:31.000Z","msg":"出息助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98c1db46ea5d4e9642915e25aaa29822ce553dbb","tid":895118,"uid":1953